---
title: Steak & Roasted Garlic Pan Sauce with Mashed Potatoes & Broccoli
description: Serious about steak? So are our chefs! That’s why they took it to the next level by topping it with a luxurious pan sauce. Here, roasted garlic and rich beef demi-glace mingle with the fond (aka the crispy bits and drippings left in the pan after cooking the meat) to create a condiment you’ll want to drizzle over just about everything… especially the chive-flecked mashed potatoes and roasted broccoli on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/60f82a0367b2ce1a3350f0ac-e2968f9f.jpg
